83
00:06:42,158 --> 00:06:45,909
We are the worst family/friends in the whole world.

84
00:06:45,910 --> 00:06:47,764
We really should be at Lucas'.

85
00:06:47,765 --> 00:06:51,213
You're right. Just stay here for a second.

86
00:06:51,901 --> 00:06:52,948
Okay.

87
00:06:54,163 --> 00:06:57,457
When  I was a kid, I had this morning paper route.

88
00:06:57,533 --> 00:07:01,626
