124
00:08:55,892 --> 00:08:58,175
They are here for your well-being.

125
00:08:58,602 --> 00:09:01,079
We can try to make the school safer.

126
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:02,887
We can try to protect you.

127
00:09:02,888 --> 00:09:07,013
But there are no precautions that we can take to heal your hearts.

128
00:09:08,988 --> 00:09:10,051
Hey.

129
00:09:11,180 --> 00:09:12,230
Hey.

130
00:09:13,395 --> 00:09:15,535
Let's just go to class, okay?

131
00:09:16,186 --> 00:09:17,238
Come on.

132
00:09:17,552 --> 00:09:19,253
I urge you to reach out 

