209
00:14:14,637 --> 00:14:16,706
Luke, when I said that...

210
00:14:19,326 --> 00:14:22,537
Because I do, Peyton.

211
00:14:23,158 --> 00:14:26,157
But it's okay, because, um...

212
00:14:26,980 --> 00:14:30,579
