225
00:15:13,907 --> 00:15:15,178
It is.

226
00:15:16,280 --> 00:15:18,809
Let Brooke help you out with this, okay?

227
00:15:18,810 --> 00:15:19,930
Don't shut her out.

228
00:15:19,931 --> 00:15:21,106
